{"tid":2497999,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"香港直播主打殘中方後再喊「台灣鳳梨」 中国玩家崩潰狂罵","createTime":"2021-04-21T01:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T02:17:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c4a7cae063f5d285c54fc16153ad6145a9d9ae26","tid":2497999,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"開放世界動作冒險遊戲《盜賊之海》在推出後頗受好評，遊戲中玩家們必須齊心合作，共同駕駛船隻在大海遨遊，進攻或抵禦來自世界各個角落的玩家。香港遊戲實況主「Ko」在擊沉一艘中國玩家駕駛的船後，一句「我這有很多台灣來的鳳梨」竟讓對岸玩家瞬間理智斷線，爆氣開嗆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9tL4gZ0yAeO9TywclENGrQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/lP8MTGLVw5e6ys5uo4eo1w--~B/aD00NTA7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/58699b8da6deba407f01ae4cc99ba4f2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9tL4gZ0yAeO9TywclENGrQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlP8MTGLVw5e6ys5uo4eo1w--~B%2FaD00NTA7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F58699b8da6deba407f01ae4cc99ba4f2&h=3860f75e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKo一行人碰上先前交戰過的中國玩家，雙方再次交戰。（圖／Twitch頻道Ko0416授權）<br />\n<br />\n實況主Ko時常在Twitch頻道開啟直播與觀眾互動，19日晚間與其他實況主組隊遊玩《盜賊之海》時，碰見了先前交戰過的中國玩家，理所當然雙方又打了起來。<br />\n<br />\n在經過一段時間的交戰後，Ko所屬一方以優勢火力再次取勝。隊友先是在公開頻道嘲諷，Ko則拿起遊戲中的大聲公喊話「老鐵你還行嗎？要上船嗎？」至此都沒有獲得對岸玩家任何回應，接著繼續說道「我這有很多台灣來的鳳梨，好吃的」，不料此舉瞬間觸動了中國玩家敏感又脆弱的神經。<br />\n<br />\n提到「台灣」兩個字，該名中國玩家便開始崩潰飆罵一連串髒話，讓Ko無奈表示「一聽到台灣就高潮我也沒辦法」。此外，面對隊友在公共頻道的嘲諷，中國玩家也打字回擊「SB台灣」、「只配吃外國的屎」。<br />\n<br />\n直播片段：<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/videos/993030129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fvideos%2F993030129&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ6gSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=18810d04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/videos/993030129</a>（約5：14：30開始）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/他喊-台灣鳳梨-中國玩家崩潰狂罵-112502451.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E4%BB%96%E5%96%8A-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%B3%B3%E6%A2%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0%E7%8B%82%E7%BD%B5-112502451.html&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ6gSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=6fb9463a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/他喊-台灣鳳梨-中國玩家崩潰狂罵-112502451.html</a>"},{"pid":"3bc9b8e4063b597fa7214f1df3de4ba9bf21d8f3","tid":2497999,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:04:57.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa75436b5a53af1c4c292ad127bbc14542ed3384","tid":2497999,"uid":9708,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:06:35.000Z","msg":"「一聽到台灣就高潮我也沒辦法」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebd3567deb1c4bd7dee29989bac66a457ee1de7","tid":2497999,"uid":60145,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:14:09.000Z","msg":"Taiwan No. 1@"},{"pid":"31a2cc5e56daabedd2b22412624aaddfbfbdb9bd","tid":2497999,"uid":11291,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVApoq6VAShaDrvu9bAugEcQuz6FCK3xDURW42iiMNJbs?filename=QHLBAaC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHLBAaC.jpg&h=2e0bbadd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5177df0d73e2b76f067ad58ce2117a089f81fdd5","tid":2497999,"uid":104044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:26:49.000Z","msg":"間中有睇下佢直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2675e3cd467750d74a4e69a9c34be1eac9cf1a","tid":2497999,"uid":29052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31a2cc5e56daabedd2b22412624aaddfbfbdb9bd","tid":2497999,"uid":11291,"like"